{"tid":1860850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文物撚請進） 二級歷史建築深水埗警署被掟火魔","createTime":"2020-02-04T01:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T02:36:31.000Z","uid":25240,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"315ac4c4a58dd44d53b05800441e9a69d01733b9","tid":1860850,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T01:45:56.000Z","msg":"欽州街深水埗警署車場出入口旁一個巴士站，清晨5時許，疑被人掟汽油彈縱火，巡警發現事件。馬路慢線留有玻璃碎片，行人路上留有少量布碎。現場消息指，一名男子向警署掟3個汽油彈，其中兩個擊中圍牆反彈，剩下一個掟入警署停車場，沒有人受傷。案件列作縱火。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200204/Q5PWB3EFPQUORNFQHVOCGVNGNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200204%2FQ5PWB3EFPQUORNFQHVOCGVNGNQ%2F&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=fb29fe1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200204%2FQ5PWB3EFPQUORNFQHVOCGVNGNQ%2F&h=c66d70ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200204/Q5PWB3EFPQUORNFQHVOCGVNGNQ/</a>"},{"pid":"987f176298669e9ca498b9aede4778fb6481e79e","tid":1860850,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"有冇識呢d 文物撚既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqMpKVa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqMpKVa.png&h=4088c495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100007995969636/posts/2551165991826575/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100007995969636%2Fposts%2F2551165991826575%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=9b97c117\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100007995969636/posts/2551165991826575/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"99327f439f4c412e73c1d81331a9ad53f44a3c65","tid":1860850,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T01:49:41.000Z","msg":"仲有呢條曆史價值